title: Astros Favored Over Phillies to Win World Series
description: Houston and Philadelphia will face off in a matchup of teams that have caught fire in the postseason. Game 1 is set for Friday in Houston.
dc:creator: Benjamin Hoffman
media:credit: Johnny Milano for The New York Times
media:description: Jose Altuve, Yuli Gurriel and the Houston Astros are back in the World Series for the fourth time in six seasons.
